# Wazuh Home SOC Lab

## Overview

This project documents my home Security Operations Center (SOC) lab built using Wazuh, Kali Linux, and Ubuntu Server. 

The objective is to simulate common attacker techniques, generate security events, and investigate alerts within the Wazuh dashboard.

## Lab Architecture

- Ubuntu Server (Wazuh Manager + Dashboard)
- Kali Linux (Attacker)
- Ubuntu Server (Monitored Endpoint with Wazuh Agent)

## Technologies

- Wazuh
- Ubuntu Server
- Kali Linux
- Linux
- SSH
- Nmap

## Current Scenarios

- [x] SSH Authentication
- [x] Privilege Escalation
- [x] File Integrity Monitoring
- [x] User Account Creation
- [x] Package Installation
- [x] Threat Hunting
- [x] Vulnerability Management (Nessus Essentials)
